There was a relationship
between Iraq and al Qaeda.

01:15:47.451 --> 01:15:49.783
Saddam. Al Qaeda.
Saddam. Al Qaeda.

01:15:49.953 --> 01:15:53.354
Saddam. The al Qaeda. Saddam.
Saddam. Saddam. Al Qaeda.

01:15:53.523 --> 01:15:55.923
It's only a matter of time
before terrorist states...

01:15:56.093 --> 01:15:58.118
...armed with weapons
of mass destruction...

01:15:58.295 --> 01:16:01.822
...develop the capability to deliver
those weapons to U.S. cities.

